  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At 'Only Pinball' you can expect pinball tables in the style of the 80s, 90s and modern.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You get realistic physics, elaborately modeled tables, atmospheric lighting, high-quality sounds and exciting themes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or with up to 4 friends and chase the high score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust the strength of your pinball fingers and choose one of the 3 settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, you can also play with 5 balls if 3 balls aren't enough for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only Pinball is a pinball collection that is continually being expanded. Exciting new topics as well as improved classics from “Malzbie’s Pinball Collection” will be found here.<br><br>At the moment, 5 pinball tables have been completed and are fully playable. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At 'Only Pinball' you can expect pinball tables in the style of the 80s, 90s and modern.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You get realistic physics, elaborately modeled tables, atmospheric lighting, high-quality sounds and exciting themes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or with up to 4 friends and chase the high score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust the strength of your pinball fingers and choose one of the 3 settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, you can also play with 5 balls if 3 balls aren't enough for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only Pinball is a pinball collection that is continually being expanded. Exciting new topics as well as improved classics from “Malzbie’s Pinball Collection” will be found here.<br><br>At the moment, 5 pinball tables have been completed and are fully playable. </p>",
  "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong>, French, Italian, German, Spanish - Spain, Portuguese - Portugal<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support",
